data.description: Cozy home nestled in a tranquil neighborhood just minutes away from the serene Wonder Lake. This charming residence offers a plethora of features that make it the perfect place to call home.  Upon entering, you'll be greeted by spacious ,sunny living room.The heart of this home is the spacious eat-in kitchen, which ample counter space, and an open layout.  Bathroom that boasts a luxurious jacuzzi tub, providing you with a spa-like oasis to unwind and relax after a long day. The hardwood floors throughout the house.Big laundry room.  Additional highlights of this property include a convenient garage, providing shelter for your vehicle and extra storage space, as well as a fenced yard, offering privacy and security for both children and pets. The yard is perfect for outdoor activities, gardening.Nice deck. 3108 Hillside Drive is more than just a house; it's a place where memories are made. Its combination of charming details, practical amenities, and its proximity to Wonder Lake make it an ideal choice for those seeking a peaceful and comfortable lifestyle. Don't miss your chance to make this lovely house your forever home.
